data.description:
leading Yacht Charter service provider of South Florida and all your favorite Miami destinations. Miami, Fort Lauderdale & Bahamas Yacht Charters are our specialty. For an unforgettable half-day, full day or a sunset cruise, let our captain and crew cater to your every desire.  When you are ready to plan the trip to your ultimate destination, let us be your guide. Simply contact us at (888) 484-5959 and we will do all of the work for you. 

Our goal is to treat you and your valued guests as royalty and to make sure you are treated to an experience only Miami 5 Star Yachts can provide. Our Captains are highly trained professionals who posses the charisma that clients come back for again and again.

We offer a large selection of Charters with each tailored to your desire. Whether you want to relax in the sun, explore Miami / Ft Lauderdale / Bahamas, discover beautiful islands, enjoy a fishing trip, or celebrate a special event in your life, we definitely have a charter for you!

Please follow us: https://www.facebook.com/Miami.Yacht.Charters.Rentals
